          There are features I'm interested in adding and I'd like to fix the drag and drop issue, but
          that would be at some undetermined, future time.
        </p>
        <p class="h5">Known Issues</p>
        <p>There are known issues in Firefox and IE11 (see below). There are no known issues in Chrome.</p>
